title: Radiohead No Electricity (Acoustic Collection) 1996 (Re-Uploaded
description:
(Re-Uploaded as the first version developed some kind of seeding error, apologies)
A collection of acoustic songs by Radiohead from 1992-1996. For the most part the quality is very good although the sources vary from track to track. Most of the tracks are from Pablo Honey and The Bends with a few from OK Computer and some random wild cards too, it's all great stuff.
